ConstraintSeverity

SHALL applications comply with this constraint?

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/constraint-severity

CodeDisplayDefinition
errorIf the constraint is violated, the resource is not conformant.
warningIf the constraint is violated, the resource is conformant, but it is not necessarily following best practice.

name: ConstraintSeverity
description: SHALL applications comply with this constraint?
